    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, you're saying i should take half my basal dose? i thought basal was supposed to be the steady amount that keeps me level regardless of what i eat. if i only take half, won't my blood sugar just spike really high by tomorrow morning? i'm confused if i should just skip it entirely or try the half dose thing you mentioned.",
